| Dimension        | Positive Effects                                                                 | Negative Effects                                                                 |
|------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Economic**     | - Market expansion and growth<br>- Job creation and poverty reduction<br>- Innovation and competition<br>- Access to capital and resources | - Job displacement and wage pressure<br>- Increased inequality<br>- Economic crisis contagion<br>- Exploitation and social dumping |
| **Cultural**     | - Cultural exchange and tolerance<br>- Access to information and communication<br>- Cultural adaptation and hybridization | - Cultural homogenization and Westernization<br>- Loss of cultural identity<br>- Spread of harmful ideologies and violence |
